{"tid":2206080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"康文署泳池明日重開 除了游泳，淋浴及往返更衣室外 泳客全程須戴口罩","createTime":"2020-09-17T09:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T10:57:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"351770cbd49297c70bf4d830f5a7be427a40049a","tid":2206080,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"康樂及文化事務署（康文署）在9月16日宣布，因應2019冠狀病毒病的最新情況，部分康樂場地和博物館將分階段於9月18日（星期五）起陸續重新開放，而游泳池亦是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n康文署亦提醒市民身處任何泳池範圍內須任何時間一直佩戴口罩，但在5個情況下可以豁免：<br />\n<br />\n游泳<br />\n淋浴<br />\n往返更衣室及泳池<br />\n往返不同泳池<br />\n在與其他人之間相距至少1.5米的情況下進行熱身運動時<br />\n<br />\n但有網民在討論區回應：「多此一舉。」，亦有網民表示：「其實身處任何泳池範圍，都是處於以上5個情況。」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/127114/%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE-%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0-%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0-%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%98-%E6%B3%B3%E7%81%98-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BA%B7%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B2.htm?fbclid=IwAR1U0-p0Xe1HxIq1W7SWZ2AE8gNRYi1Epnovr4qRJqgR1DunoJmY41PvaZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstimes.com.hk%2Farticles%2F127114%2F%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E6%25B1%25A0-%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E6%25B1%25A0-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%2598-%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E7%2581%2598-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BD%25B2.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1U0-p0Xe1HxIq1W7SWZ2AE8gNRYi1Epnovr4qRJqgR1DunoJmY41PvaZU&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=ebc100bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/127114/%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE-%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0-%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0-%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%98-%E6%B3%B3%E7%81%98-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BA%B7%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B2.htm?fbclid=IwAR1U0-p0Xe1HxIq1W7SWZ2AE8gNRYi1Epnovr4qRJqgR1DunoJmY41PvaZU</a>"},{"pid":"05ca10cb18987c19468d16e43709855dc18870db","tid":2206080,"uid":147047,"l